text: Jeanne Sandford (born 30 September 1926) was a British alpine skier. She competed in two events at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1926 births Category:Living people Category:British female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Great Britain Category:Alpine skiers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
